<html lang='en'><head><meta charset='UTF-8' /><meta
      name='viewport'
      content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0'
    /><style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      h1 {
        color: #f57c00;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      h2 {
        color: #1565c0;
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 18px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
      .section {
        background-color: #e0e0e0;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #333333;
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .highlight {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #1565c0;
      }
      a.button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        background-color: #f57c00;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style></head><body><div class='container'><h1>Welcome to Quest,
        {{firstName}}
        {{lastName}}!</h1><p>We’re excited to have you join our platform. Here’s a summary of your
        application:</p><div class='section'><p><span class='highlight'>Role Applied:</span>
          {{roleApplied}}</p><p><span class='highlight'>Application Status:</span>
          {{applicationStatus}}</p><p><span class='highlight'>Tech Stack:</span> {{techStack}}</p><p
        ><span class='highlight'>Start Date:</span> {{startDate}}</p></div><p>Next steps:</p><ul><li
        >Complete your profile and onboarding tasks</li><li>Explore our learning resources</li><li
        >Connect with your mentor for guidance</li></ul><a
        href='https://www.questapp.com/start'
        class='button'
      >Get Started</a><div class='footer'>Need help? Reply to this email or contact
        support@questapp.com</div></div></body></html>